              #sample-form
                h4 Forms

                p.align-justify.
                  Probably all websites and apps will contain (at least) one form, so,
                  that's why <code class="primary">seed-css</code> has a really simple, easy to use and customizable
                  form field stylesheet. Have a look on the examples below:

