                  Media queries allows us to make an even more accurated design. In <code class="primary">seed-css</code>
                  they are made to represent the following screen sizes:

                table
                  thead
                    tr
                      th &nbsp;
                      th Screen width
                      th Prefix
                      th Columns
                      th Container
                  tbody
                    tr
                      td.nowrap Mobiles
                      td.nowrap
                        strong &lt; 600px
                      td.nowrap
                        strong .sm
                      td
                        strong 12
                      td
                        strong 90%
                    tr
                      td.nowrap Tablets
                      td.nowrap
                        strong &lt;= 990px
                      td.nowrap
